Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: You heard him, %playername%.░ Whaddaya say?░ Down for a quickie?
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: <i>I sighed,░ I didn't want to make a bad situation any worse░ and I could read all the signs that there was something else going on here.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
<i>You know what?░ Fuck it.░
I came out to this club to have a good time,░ and a good time was being presented to me.░ It might have seemed like the two of them had something to work out there, but that wasn't my problem.░
I gave them both an eager smile.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Are you fucking serious?░ Ugh, what a waste of time.░ You promised me you could hook me up with anyone, Zenith.░ It looks like your 'charm' wasn't enough this time.
Events.Title: Rose Wood

Events.Text: <i>I was taken aback by the sudden outburst.░ The brunt of Rose's complaints seemed to be wtih Zenith,░ had they made some sort of bet?░ They muttered back and forth for a moment:░ Zenith said Rose had promised not to do this;░ Rose said Zenith was being a bitch, as usual.░ I was about to leave them to their whispered fight when the girly avian shot me one last glare and stormed off,░ but not before snatching up his drink from nearby and emptying it on Zenith's shirt.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
I'm going to go find Zack.░
And don't go thinking you can join in this time, Zenith.░
Ciao, bitches.
Events.Title: Rose Wood

Events.Text: <i>What a scene.░ I had no idea what was going on,░ but Zenith certainly looked upset.░ The charming,░ cocky bouncer that I first met was replaced with someone else entirely.░ He folded his arms across the wet patch on his broad chest,░ looking to the side and grimacing as he fought to regain his cool.░ He took a moment,░ caught his breath,░ and forced a smile.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Heh,░ I'm sorry about all that, %playername%.░ You shouldn't have gotten roped into that mess.░ Tell you what,░ next time I see you I owe you an apology drink.░ As for right now... think I'm gonna call it a bad night and go home.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text:
<i>Since I'd met him,░ Zenith seemed at his most genuine now:░ even clearly simmering and humiliated.░ It seemed like, whatever it was that was going on,░ it had been Rose's game, not his.░ Part of me wanted to find out what exactly had happened,░ an even larger part if Rose and Zenith were an item,░ because he really shouldn't be...░
But was it really my business?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>Perhaps it was best to let Zenith figure things out on his own.░ I let him head off while I wandered back to the dance floor.░ Maybe this wasn't going to be as easy as Coby had said...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>There's no way I can leave things like this.░ Before the dragon could make his escape into the staff only room,░ I caught his wrist.░ Zenith cocked his head back at me over his shoulder as I let go,░ maybe not the best time to be grabbing him more?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Look.░ I know it's not my place,░ but obviously something serious just happened.░ I can't let you walk off like that in good conscience.░ Do you want to sit down and talk about it?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
So,░ if he's out of the picture,░ you and I can hook up, right?░
I've had my eye on you since I came over,░ you know.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Haha, but why buy me a drink later when you can buy me a drink now?░ Hell, you can buy me two drinks! ░ I'll even buy YOU a drink!░ What do you say...?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Are you fuckin' joking right now?░ I'm pretty sure you were here when that shitstorm went down.░ You really think I wanna bone right now?
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text:
<i>He looked pretty pissed off,░ I got the impression it wasn't just getting riled up by his friend either.░
He could take me down in a second flat,░ and I'm pretty sure I don't want to test that theory.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Maybe it's for the best,░ you know?░ I'm not sure if I could handle sharing you right now.░ One on one time is the best way to push each other's limits I found.░ Care to try, stud?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Oh I'm so not in the fuckin' mood for this shit!
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text:
<i>Before I knew it there was a hot flash of light,░ and a spreading pain in my snout.░
I had the sensation of looking up, up, up with my whole body.░ My last thought before I hit the floor was: 'did he just punch my head off?'.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
<i>I woke up on the asphalt.░ It didn't seem too long since,░ but if I'd walked outside he'd punched that memory right out of me like a skipped record.░
I'd pushed my luck stupidly and paid the price for it.░
Hopefully I'd still get that free drink he promised me.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Hey... I'm sorry.░ That joke was in bad taste.░ I was just trying to lighten the mood a little.░ I don't know exactly what happened there,░ but I do mean it when I say that you far out-class him...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>Zenith closed his eyes, sighed, and showed me that big toothy grin.░ Without Rose checking in on him, it felt a lot more real this time.░ He pointed to the stairs then held out his hand for me.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Gonna need that drink,░ and a fresh start, yeah?░ The name's Zenith.░ To whom do I owe the pleasure?
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: <i>That toothy grin never left Zenith's face.░ I didn't know him well enough to know if he was faking it or not as he extended his hand for a handshake.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
<i>I extend my hand sharing his grin,░ playing along for the time being.░ 
His grip was like a vice, damn!░ Maybe I'd earned a little bit of a squeezing after jumping in on Rose's game though.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>With a shake of my head I smiled at him.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Bahaha!░ Hmmm, it's strange, isn't it?░ Must be fate playing tricks on us.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: You're no fun, %playername%.░ But I get where you're coming from.░ Eyes on the prize, yeah?
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: <i>Zenith retracted his vice-like hand and laughed again,░ starting toward the stairs with me following him.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>I busied myself with my own drink.░ I was a little surprised by what I'd ordered,░ but I suppose I was more concerned about getting Zenith over what had happened with Rose.░ Zenith chuckled, rolling his glass between his palms a little.░ When he looked back he seemed a little embarrassed.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Thanks, %playername%,░ I mean it.░ I'm just a stranger...░
Hell,░ a stranger who was sort of leading you on a little.░ You didn't have to reach out and see if I was okay.░
You're kind of one of those good ones, huh?
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text:
Honestly, don't worry about it.░ I saw that something was wrong and wanted to make sure you were ok.░
Besides, even if we were moving a little quick there,░ we're not strangers anymore,░ right?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: So what was the deal with Rose, anyways?░ You acted so differently when you were around him.░ It's almost like you were a different person.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: You're welcome.░ I'm glad you're feeling better now.░ If things are all patched up, you wouldn't mind if I headed back out into the club, would you?░ The night is still young, after all.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: No worries!░ Anyway...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Y'know, that's right.░ I guess that's one positive thing that came out of this shit.░ Thanks, %playername%.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: I...░ I'd prefer if we didn't talk about that right now.░ I'm enjoying myself at the moment.░ Perhaps another time?
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: Oh.░ You gotta go so soon?░ I mean, if you've gotta go you gotta go.░ But I was hoping for a chance to prove I'm not a total scumbag before you go.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text:
Another time maybe, I need to head off.░ I'm here with my brother and I we weren't planning to stay too late.░ I'm really glad we smoothed things over before you left.░
Take care of yourself, Zenith
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Damn,░ shame you gotta go, but it was nice meeting you, %playername%.░ I feel a lot better after you stopped me,░ and for that I thank ya.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text:
<i>Zenith and I shared a smile, but the conversation felt done with.░ I guess if it's meant to be I'll catch him around,░ but I didn't want to rush into getting his number when he was in the middle of whatever it is he had to work out with Rose.░
Now,░ back to the nightlife for me...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>Despite our initial introductions, he seemed like a good guy.░ What was the harm in talking a little bit,░ it'd certainly be better than just writing off the whole attempt to make new friends.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Sure,░ let's change the subject.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: So, Zenith.░ Tell me a little about yourself.░ Have you been a bouncer here for long?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Y'know, I would've never expected to be in this situation.░ I feel like so much has happened for my being here a pretty short while.░ Is it always this crazy?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I'm curious though.░ Just for my own ego's sake...░ Did you mean any of that stuff you said about me before?░
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Hah,░ well, I've been a bouncer here since the place opened up.░ Trust me, I've seen some crazy shit go down that makes what happened earlier look like a party:░ fights, break-ups, orgies; even a robbery.░ Well, almost a robbery.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: That's the part that caught your interest?░ Regardless, yeah... couple of punks tried to rob some VIPs one night,░ with switchblades no less.░ Luckily, me and one of the other bouncers managed to take them down before anyone got hurt.░ Turns out that all the cop training was good for something after all.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: Wait, you saw this place get robbed?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: You think this is a big deal?░ Hah, it can be quieter, but I've also seen way worse.░ Been bouncing in this place since it first opened.░ I've seen fights, break-ups, orgies; hell,░ I even saw the place get robbed once.░ Well, almost robbed.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text:
<i>...Hold on.
Orgies?! Should I feel even more worried about Coby coming here so often?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>Zenith cocked his eyebrow.░ He leaned over a bit more so he could close the gap between us.░ That signature grin was back:░ I had to hand it to him,░ he had a really nice smile.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: For your ego huh?░ Well, tell this to your ego...
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: <i>He gave a little wink and we toasted to that.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
I don't know if 'cute' quite covers it,░ though you being fresh-faced maybe had something to do with that.░ But, yeah, I meant it,░ and I'm glad you're cool enough to sit and get a drink after too.░
Hey,░ so let's change the subject for now, huh?░ I'm gonna be leaving the bar by myself,░ I don't wanna go down this line of inquiry again today.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: <i>Zenith's modesty was humbling,░ he was so casual and relaxed as he talked about taking down a bunch of guys with knives.░ I had to note that his arm flexing subtly as he told the story proved how well he could handle himself,░ it was weird that he'd settle for being a club bouncer with a body like his.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: So, you used to be a cop huh?░ I mean, from the looks of you,░ I can definitely see it.░
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I should probably start heading out now, though.░ I want to see what my brother Coby is up to.░ I really enjoyed meeting you though, Zenith.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: The feeling is mutual, %playername%.░ I don't think I've ever had such a casual conversation with someone at this club before.░ If you ever want to meet up again sometime, just give this number a ring.░ Besides, I still owe you a drink.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: <i>The Dragon gives me that huge, toothy grin one last time before patting me on the back and heading into the staff only section.░ Oof.░ Felt like a damn earthquake.░ If I ever want that drink, I'll be sure to give that number a call.░ For now, back into the nightlife...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>The moment I said those words,░ he lowered his flexing arm and washed his fading grin away entirely with a gulp of his beer.░ He seemed like he'd seen a ghost,░ I suppose he did have his reasons then?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Let's pretend I never brought that up, alright?░
Seriously,░ drop it, yeah?░ For me.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: So, break-ups I can imagine.░ But just how many orgies have you seen here?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>I smiled warmly as the color returned to his face bit by bit.░ A brief, but noticeable nod as he composed himself.░ He clapped me on the back with a large hand: once, twice, three times.░ He was a jackhammer of platitudes that was likely to leave a bruise if he wasn't careful.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Ha!░ More orgies than I think either of us could handle in a lifetime.░ But seriously,░ I don't think I've had a proper, casual conversation with someone here for a while.░ Thanks for that, I ain't exactly used to it, but it's relaxing.░ I owe you.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text:
<i>Zenith reached into his pocket and pulled out a small notepad and pen.░
He scribbled his number onto the pad and tore off the sheet, handing it over.░
I took it and Zenith finished his drink as I programmed it into my phone,░ pushing off from the bar when he was done.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Give me a call sometime, %playername%.░ I need to unwind after tonight's shit show, and you're fun to be around.░ Gonna head out now, but don't leave me hanging too long, yeah?
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text:
<i>Well it certainly was an encounter I wasn't going to forget any time soon.░ I guess he was worth calling back?░
For now,░ the night was still young.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: It can't be that bad, can it?░ I mean, I'm sorry if you got fired or something?░ I've got some pretty funny stories about jobs I've gotten fired from, if you wanna hear about those...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>Zenith didn't say a word.░ He simply pulled out a pen and tore a scrap off a notepad in his pocket.░ I wasn't sure if he was writing down what had happened,░ but he was done too quick for that.░ He finished his drink and slammed the glass down with a controlled clap against the polished bar before walking off.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
<i>The paper had his phone number on it,░ and under it: 'Let me cool off first.'░
I guess I owe him an apology...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
'Sup, guys.░
The name's %playername%.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>If I kept grinning,░ they'll definitely cave in and realize that I'm more interesting than whatever it is they have going on here.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>Any second now,░ the cute avian was already in on it,░ the dragon guy was sure to break too.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>Here it comes! The big payoff for me playing it so cool...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Hey, you two,░ my name is %playername%.░ I'm kind of new to the whole club scene and I figured I'd say hi,░ if I'm not interrupting, that is?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I'm sorry,░ I, uh...░ I'm new to this whole 'club' thing.░ I've not really got the approaching people coolly part down yet...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: It's %playername%...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I think I'll measure up.░ The name's %playername%, by the way.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Hi,░ I'm %playername%,░ pleasure to meet the both of you.░ Actually I've not been here too much much, it's basically my first time here.░ Hell, it's my first time at any club...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Yeah?░ I'm surprised I didn't see someone as handsome as you sooner.░ Though I can understand you were already pretty distracted by your friend here.░ I don't blame you there.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
I...░
Well, thank you.░ I'm not really used to handsome guys like you calling me cute right off the bat.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Alright...░ I've got to ask, why are you guys making all these passes at me?░ I mean, we only just met after all. You don't do this with every curious person you meet,░ do you?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Alright.░ I know where this is going.░ I didn't come out tonight for a quick fuck with two complete strangers.░
Can we start over?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: You guys aren't too bad looking yourselves.░ How about we get some drinks?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: So, guys...░ Do you do this often with every new stud that walks in?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Y'know, I'm starting to have second thoughts about all this.░ It's starting to seem like you two do this with every curious person you meet...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Think you two can keep up with me?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Why are you two doing this?░ We just met.░ You don't do this with every curious person you meet,░ do you?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Wait, what do you mean remember who's number one?░ It's starting to seem like you two do this with every curious person you meet...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I'm not really the number one, 'alpha personality' kind of person... But I don't mind a little competition on who can be the most... accommodating.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I think that'd be good for all of us.░ When and where?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Look, guys...░
I'm going to have to pass.░ Thanks for being so friendly with me tonight, though.░ It really means a lot,░ I didn't expect to meet so many nice people here.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
You can call me %playername%!░
For some reason,░ I feel like we've met before.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
We don't have to start over,░ I'm still glad to have met you.░
Anyway, if we started over,░ you wouldn't owe me that drink!
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Meet us in the back,░ sweetheart.░ I'm just going to freshen up a bit...
Events.Title: Rose Wood

Events.Text:
<i>I waited out in the back of the club for who knows how long.░ Fifteen minutes at least?░
It wasn't cold but standing around as I watched others chatting░ (a few other hook-ups too, it looked like)░ it started to wear on me as my blood cooled.░ Maybe I'd been too hasty after all?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Hey, Rose,░ where's Zenith?░ I thought...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>I was quickly cut off,░ a look of impatient lust plastered all over his face.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Oh,░ sorry honey...░ I found someone else as we were leaving.░ I felt bad though,░ couldn't help but come to break the news to you...
Events.Title: Rose Wood

Events.Text:
<i>After he finished speaking,░ he peered over to the guy by the car who adjusted his pants.░ Rose let out a sultry moan,░ those hips wiggling a little.░
He didn't seem sorry in the slightest.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Maybe next time,░ cutie.░ 
I've got the feeling I'll be busy all night though...
Events.Title: Rose Wood

Events.Text:
<i>Before I could even say a word,░ he was off.░ I pushed my way back inside so I didn't have to hear Rose giggling all the way back to the car.░
I should've known something was up from the moment I met those two,░ and it didn't seem like Zenith was that welcome in Rose's evening plans either.░
I grit my teeth. Stupid.░ Lesson learned:░ if it seems too good to be true,░ it usually is.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>At least I had an amusing story to tell Coby, I guess.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Mm, I think so.░ She's absolutely adorable...
Never one to turn down fresh meat either.
Events.Title: Rose Wood

Events.Text:
Mm, I think so.░ They're absolutely adorable...
Never one to turn down fresh meat either.
Events.Title: Rose Wood

Events.Text: You must've been poured into these, huh?░ Is it hard to get you out of them again?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>He gave a little gasp at my touch,░ biting his lower lip in response.░ I couldn't help but feel that,░ despite my boldness,░ that gasp was more than a little faked for Zenith's benefit.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>Zenith moved closer,░ reaching an arm around both his friend and me at the same time.░ He scooped me closer, chest-to-chest with the avian between our toned bodies. Maybe being pec-to-pec was a little premature,░ but I suppose I did instigate.░ The other guy, Rose, made a little 'eep' nose before snuggling up to Zenith,░ winking at me with a smirk.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>I looking between him and Zenith,░ he had the same look of playful hunger in his bright green eyes despite how he hugged Rose a little tighter to him than myself, reining him in a little maybe?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Mm, yeah...░ I like someone who's willing to take charge.░ But you knew that already...
Events.Title: Rose Wood

Events.Text: Mm, yeah...░ I like a girl who can take charge.░ But you knew that already...
Events.Title: Rose Wood

Events.Text: I mean, okay, yeah:░ she's cute and all...░ but don't forget who's cuter, Zenith.░ She'll do,░ so long as you remember who's number one.
Events.Title: Rose Wood

Events.Text: I mean, okay, yeah:░ they're cute and all...░ but don't forget who's cuter, Zenith.░ They'll do,░ so long as you remember who's number one.
Events.Title: Rose Wood

Events.Text: A first timer?░ And looking sharp in that suit to boot?░ Oh, what ever shall we do with our Casanova here...
Events.Title: Rose Wood

Events.Text: A first timer?░ And looking just adorable in those girly clothes too?░ Oh, what ever to do with a pretty picture like that.
Events.Title: Rose Wood

Events.Text: A first timer?░ I suppose that makes sense from the rough and ready outfit...░ Oh, what ever to do with a tough cookie like you.
Events.Title: Rose Wood

Events.Text: A first timer?░ You'd never guess from how you're flaunting everything there!░ Oh, what ever to do with a slinky number like that.
Events.Title: Rose Wood

Events.Text:
Oh, hey, %playername% right?░ I was wondering if you'd work up the courage to come back and keep chatting.░
I'm sorry t' scare you off,░ cute though it is watching you fluster and scurry off.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: Oh, hey, %playername% right?░ I was wondering if you'd work up the courage to come back.░ Did you end up thinking about our little proposal any?
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: Oh, hey, if it isn't the Cheshire Prat.░ I was wondering if you'd work up the courage to come back and talk to us like a normal fucking person.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: Now you've really intrigued me...
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: I think I can measure up.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Funny thing is, I believe you.░ Think we've found what we're looking for, Rose?
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: <i>I should definitely avoid that guy tonight...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Yeah...░ Can we chalk that up to me being a colossal idiot newbie?░ I'm sorry guys,░ either the drinks here are stronger than I expected or I'm so rusty at this stuff I just sank.░ I'm %playername%, by the way.░ Thanks for not, you know... kicking my ass?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Awww, honey your ass isn't quite safe yet I don't think... But I can overlook the being dumb ass on account of that being the cutest apology I've ever heard.░ And because a little leverage goes a long way if you're hoping to make it up to us...
Events.Title: Rose Wood

Events.Text:
Yeah, shit, I guess everyone has a fuck up day.░
You're on thin ice newbie... and that's only because that blush suits you to a T.░
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: <i>I threw my hands out, stopping the advance of the beefy security guard, my cool facade well and truly broken.░ The two of them stopped in place as if deciding what type of crazy person I was:░ dangerous or just profoundly dumb.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
<i>Zenith clapped one large palm on my back.░
Damn,░ the guy certainly could pack a punch,░ I wasn't exactly a lightweight, but the security guard certainly gave me a run for my money.░ Regardless,░ they sure didn't waste any time being friendly:░ I guess Coby's advice about being more open paid off.░ I couldn't help but smile despite my shiness.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
<i>I was ready to check my phone,░ give them another few minutes before I went to look for them,░ when Rose stepped out with someone else.░
Zenith didn't seem to be with him, it was a wolf who he was on the arm of.░ Rose pat the handsome guy square on the bulge in his shorts to stop him at his car before coming back over.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Failure
Events.Title: [Editor Comment]

Events.Text: Failure.
Events.Title: [Editor Comment]

Events.Text: Failure.
Events.Title: [Editor Comment]

Events.Text: Failure.
Events.Title: [Editor Comment]

Events.Text: <i>We took our place at the bar and Zenith took my order.░ We were served almost instantly thanks to his staff shirt.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
<i>After the first sip of his beer,░ the frustration still smoldering under the surface seemed to have cooled enough that Zenith didn't seem on the verge of punching a wall or something.░
He savored the mild bubbles,░ exhaled and we both seemed to come to the realization that I'd be staring at him a little.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>Zenith still seemed like he was on duty.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Hey, %playername%.░
You're still here huh?░ Doing ok?
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text:
I just wanted to see if you were running that game again with another newbie...░
I hope that things with Rose opened your eyes a little,░ messing with me like that was wrong.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Message received,░ we done here or did you have some more salt to rub in that wound?░
Enjoy the rest of your night.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text:
<i>He didn't seem that interested in hearing if I did have more to say as he slipped into the staff room with a calm, but calculated thud of the door.░
At least I told him what I thought.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I just wanted to say thanks for earlier.░ I know tonight wasn't exactly normal fare.░ But you handled it like a gentleman and I'm glad I met you.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I just wanted to check how you were, Zenith?░ It didn't seem like tonight was normal fare for you either.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
That's fine.░
Sorry it went down like it did, but I'm glad it didn't spoil your night.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text:
Actually, bitchy queens throwing their drinks on me is about a normal night for me...░
I'm doing fine though, thanks.░ Hey, don't let me ruin your night.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: <i>He sighed and smiled to himself for a moment before reaching into his back pocket and pulling out a business card.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Listen...░ I'd be kicking myself if I didn't at least ask for your number.░ For when things are cooled off, at least?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
<i>He seemed to puzzle that one out and for a moment I was really afraid he would say no.░
Our introduction wasn't exactly smooth and I really wouldn't have blamed him if he didn't want anything more to do with me.░
He reached into his back pocket and pulled out a business card, offering it my way.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
I'll catch you around!░
Take care of yourself, okay?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: You too, %playername%.░ Get home safe!
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text:
Don't usually do this,░ but it kind of feels like a makin' an exception kind of night, huh?░
Gimme a call some time, yeah?
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text: Yeah, you bet Zenith.░ Thank you.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Just...░ I dunno.░
Yeah.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text:
Yeah.░
Goodnight, Zenith.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Hey, listen.░ Speaking of being more of a gentleman,░ I hope you don't mind me asking what pronouns your prefer?░
Wouldn't wanna say the wrong thing
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text:
Hey, listen.░ Speaking of being more of a gentleman,░ I hope you don't mind me checking what pronouns you prefer?░
Wouldn't wanna say the wrong thing and given the crowd we get here, I don't wanna assume.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text:
Hey, listen.░ Speaking of being more of a gentleman,░ I hope you don't mind me checking what pronouns you prefer?░
Wouldn't wanna say the wrong thing and given the crowd we get here, I don't wanna assume that just because you're looking cute in that outfit... Well, you know.

Events.Text: <i>I nodded softly,░ at least he was being polite and asking.░ I suppose in a place like this with such a large GLBT+ crowd he'd probably met all sorts.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>I felt the heat rise to my face,░ there he went calling me cute again...░ I guess,░ considering Rose,░ he had a preference for effeminately dressed guys.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I prefer female pronouns, yeah.░ Thanks for checking, Zenith
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I prefer neutral terms,░ I sort of see myself as in the middle I guess?░ Thanks for checking, Zenith
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I prefer male pronouns, yeah.░ Thanks for checking, Zenith
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I've gotta ask,░ not that I'm not loving your company and all...░ Rose kinda spun my head a little,░ but I do know you like him. Was I going to be wasting my time trying to get with a guy like you?░ Being a girl and all.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
<i>Ah, the whole big daddy, little princess thing?░ Haha...
Nah, guys might get preferential treatment,░ but I wasn't yanking your chain or anything.░ I've played for both teams,░ just not as freqently.
Events.Title: Zenith

Events.Text:
Sure thing, Zenith.░
Thanks.
